pageProduct.name: OsteVit-D Vitamin D3 & Calcium Plus One-A-Day 110 Tablets
pageProduct.description:
General Information

OsteVit-D One-A-Day Vitamin D3 & Calcium Plus contains Vitamin D3 1000IU & Calcium 600mg PLUS 6 other nutrients

OsteVit-D One-A-Day Vitamin D3 & Calcium PLUS supports bone health & muscle function.
It contains 8 nutrients:
1. Vitamin D3 2. Calcium 3. Magnesium 4. Boron
5. Zinc 6. Copper 7. Manganese 8. Vitamin K1

Size: 60 Caplets

KEY FEATURES

• • Supports bone health and muscle function
• • Vitamin D enhances calcium absorption
• • Calcium supports bone density and strength
• • Supports healthy immune system function
• • Suitable for vegetarians
• • Free from: Gluten, Lactose, Yeast, Gelatin Artificial colours

Warnings

Vitamins can only be of assistance if dietary vitamin intake is inadequate.
Contains Sugar

Ingredients

Acacia, carmellose sodium, colloidal anhydrous silica, diethyl phthalate, dl-alpha-tocopherol, ethylcellulose, hypromellose, magnesium stearate, maize starch, medium chain triglycerides, microcrystalline cellulose, purified talc, silicon dioxide, sodium lauryl sulfate ,sucrose, titanium dioxide

Active Ingredients: Vitamin D3 - 1000IU, Calcium 600 mg, Magnesium 100 mg, Boron 1mg, Zinc 15 mg, Copper 2mg, Manganese 2mg, Vitamin K 5 microgram

Directions

Adults and children over 12 years of age: One caplet daily or as directed by your healthcare professional. Children under 12 years of age: As directed by your health professional

STORAGE INSTRUCTIONS

Store below 25°C
